{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ShiyDxh1kbheUPMtZrZ7uC","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package model\n     2→\n     3→import \"time\"\n     4→\n     5→// Run status constants.\n     6→const (\n     7→\tStatusPending   = \"pending\"\n     8→\tStatusRunning   = \"running\"\n     9→\tStatusCompleted = \"completed\"\n    10→\tStatusFailed    = \"failed\"\n    11→\tStatusCancelled = \"cancelled\"\n    12→)\n    13→\n    14→// WorkflowRun represents an instance of a workflow being executed.\n    15→type WorkflowRun struct {\n    16→\tID          string     `json:\"id\"`\n    17→\tWorkflowID  string     `json:\"workflow_id\"`\n    18→\tStatus      string     `json:\"status\"`\n    19→\tInput       string     `json:\"input\"`\n    20→\tOutput      string     `json:\"output\"`\n    21→\tCurrentStep int        `json:\"current_step\"`\n    22→\tStartedAt   *time.Time `json:\"started_at,omitempty\"`\n    23→\tCompletedAt *time.Time `json:\"completed_at,omitempty\"`\n    24→\tCreatedAt   time.Time  `json:\"created_at\"`\n    25→}\n    26→\n    27→// ActivityRun represents an instance of an activity within a workflow run.\n    28→type ActivityRun struct {\n    29→\tID             string     `json:\"id\"`\n    30→\tWorkflowRunID  string     `json:\"workflow_run_id\"`\n    31→\tActivityName   string     `json:\"activity_name\"`\n    32→\tStepIndex      int        `json:\"step_index\"`\n    33→\tStatus         string     `json:\"status\"`\n    34→\tInput          string     `json:\"input\"`\n    35→\tOutput         string     `json:\"output\"`\n    36→\tAttempts       int        `json:\"attempts\"`\n    37→\tMaxRetries     int        `json:\"max_retries\"`\n    38→\tTimeoutSeconds int        `json:\"timeout_seconds\"`\n    39→\tStartedAt      *time.Time `json:\"started_at,omitempty\"`\n    40→\tCompletedAt    *time.Time `json:\"completed_at,omitempty\"`\n    41→\tLastHeartbeat  *time.Time `json:\"last_heartbeat,omitempty\"`\n    42→\tCreatedAt      time.Time  `json:\"created_at\"`\n    43→}\n    44→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01NHF3R5g7kdFioUm6bPGqQp","session_id":"701e3a6a-36af-4762-8d76-051700988d74","uuid":"ea9b9948-25f6-43d7-a888-bbbcde4359d0"}
